WEBVTT

00:05.665 --> 00:10.036
We wanted to appeal to a wide range of personal styles,...

00:12.537 --> 00:17.523
...so with Apple Watch Edition, we're working with a uniquely luxurious metal:...

00:18.257 --> 00:20.010
...18-karat solid gold.

00:20.783 --> 00:23.950
We are using both yellow and rose gold.

00:24.465 --> 00:28.466
Each is a custom alloy designed to be not only beautiful,...

00:28.971 --> 00:31.813
...but up to twice as hard as standard gold.

00:33.481 --> 00:38.667
The result is gold that is elegant, yet uncompromisingly durable.

